            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the pouch[es] of<strong> cooked white long grain rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> white long grain</strong> <strong>rice</strong>,<strong> soy sauce </strong>and<strong> toasted sesame oil </strong>to the pan, breaking up the rice with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until all the rice is coated</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1606132808935-x200.jpg",
