            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, turn down the heat to medium-high, push the rice to one side of the pan and crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the other side</p><p>Stir the<strong> </strong>egg[s] with a wooden spoon to break the yolks and cook for 1-2 min until it resembles scrambled egg, then mix it all through the rice – this is your <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>pork &</strong> <strong>egg fried rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
