    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sesame pork & egg fried rice</strong> in bowls</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
